{"tid":734587,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"得力素糖與Avengers 無限之戰","createTime":"2018-07-08T17:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T08:14:29.000Z","uid":11598,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d0115ebf84baa254b9ea9a9fcf9c3219a43931","tid":734587,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T17:59:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://medium.com/@SiuLoBigPlace/%E5%BE%97%E5%8A%9B%E7%B4%A0%E8%88%87%E7%84%A1%E9%99%90%E4%B9%8B%E6%88%B0-%E7%84%A1%E5%8A%87%E9%80%8F-8cf0f2646f3c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40SiuLoBigPlace%2F%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%258A%259B%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%2599%2590%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%258A%2587%25E9%2580%258F-8cf0f2646f3c&d=oym2T%2F0Q7q2FF4yFJ3Qu6xFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=c6a7e677\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@SiuLoBigPlace/%E5%BE%97%E5%8A%9B%E7%B4%A0%E8%88%87%E7%84%A1%E9%99%90%E4%B9%8B%E6%88%B0-%E7%84%A1%E5%8A%87%E9%80%8F-8cf0f2646f3c</a><br />\n<br />\n電影開場後， Thanos就隨即登場，關於他的霸氣外型，眼睛除了對他的下巴很在意之外(因為入場前已看到一些帖文，說他的下巴像日常生活各種東西）；我在意的，就是一顆顆不同顏色陸續出現的無限寶石，我都覺得很像一種香港有售的糖果：得力素。<br />\n<br />\n至於得力素是怎樣的糖果呢？ 得力素是經過結晶方法做的硬糖，糖份很高，成份當中還含有葡萄糖粉，而且有幾種口味。放進口後，可以用口水含至結晶表層溶化，中心的餡就會流出舌頭，嘗到第二階段的甜味：另一種食法，就是直接把結晶咬碎，連餡全單接收落喉嚨。所以得力素的結晶外層和內在能幫人補充能量的葡萄糖粉，意外地令我聯想到得力素與無限寶石的內外特點吻合。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無限寶石還有像什麼糖果呢？其實大部分以結晶方法做的硬糖，都是無限之石的近親，例如德國的二寶、 日本的super lemon 和台灣森永水果硬糖等等。而硬糖的製作， 硬糖是經高溫熬煮而成的糖果，另外其實硬糖也有分為 透明的、半透明的和不透明的，而糖的口味，水果與牛奶也有，北歐更有甘草藥材味，基本上是層出不窮的。而本文所談的無限寶石，就應該是果汁味吧。<br />\n<br />\n未知無限寶石在電影的下一集有何下落，但是Thanos的紫色間條下巴，與得力素的舊包裝也有些相似，他骨子內的基因，也許真的很喜歡得力素。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/1500/1*JVF16ud_NcweBDQ8NC2Buw.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn-images-1.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1500%2F1%2AJVF16ud_NcweBDQ8NC2Buw.jpeg&h=0f5facac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Google 緊得力素無啦啦見到呢篇嘢，笑撚死"},{"pid":"1b65c54f3932196fd63d0dea240062cc7e6a0768","tid":734587,"uid":26711,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:04:36.000Z","msg":"我都可以整個拳套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32024f5dc2ca8c8ebb47d001bc2ddc19549059d5","tid":734587,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1b65c54f3932196fd63d0dea240062cc7e6a0768","tid":734587,"uid":26711,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:04:36.000Z","msg":"我都可以整個拳套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> i don't feel so good"},{"pid":"d13843d5390b2c7b2600726304719cd0cbbd3590","tid":734587,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f952ff62a78a963d58b9a45830f8dc62ab9586e9","tid":734587,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T19:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d4b57c8582c1ccefcfa2828530cbb3c3a2d00f","tid":734587,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T23:46:33.000Z","msg":"你好撚得閒"},{"pid":"9a1fe7936185898cbcd322d423750cb9cd691d65","tid":734587,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5d4b57c8582c1ccefcfa2828530cbb3c3a2d00f","tid":734587,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T23:46:33.000Z","msg":"你好撚得閒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:08:12.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"5992dbd9c2302d54ec85b7173a8695aeee7aad98","tid":734587,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT